        Install
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ``rolex`` is released on PyPI, so all you need is:
        
        .. code-block:: console
        
        	$ pip install rolex
        
        To upgrade to latest version:
        
        .. code-block:: console
        
        	$ pip install --upgrade rolex
